We are pleased to offer dining options to accommodate your inflight schedule.
You may select our traditional dinner served in courses,
or our Dine Upon Request'™ service,
a complete meal presented all at once, at any time you wish.
If you should choose our Dine Upon Request option
and wish to dine as soon as possible, please notify your flight attendant.
APPETIZERS
To START
Warm mixed Nuts or herbed Oyster Crackers
to accompany your preferred Cocktail or Beverage
APPETIZER SALAD
Smoked Salmon accompanied by a Cherry Tomato and Haricots Verts,
Romano Salad and seasonal mixed Greens with Cracked Black Pepper
and Romano Cheese Dressing or Orange Balsamic Vinaigrette
BREAD BASKET
Assorted warm Breads
ENTREES
FILET MIgnOn
Grilled Filet of Beef enhanced by a Tomato Parsley Demi-Glace,
served with sauteed Asparagus Tips, Mushrooms and Red Bell Peppers,
accompanied by Cheddar Whipped Potatoes
SEAFOOD RISOTTO
Creamy mixture of Rice
flavored by Seafood Medley
ROASTED CHICKEN WITH MIXED GREENS
Chilled Breast of Chicken seasoned with Marjoram,
featured with grilled Onion Salad and a fresh mixture of Spinach,
Napa Cabbage and herb-dried Tomato wedges,
enhanced by Avocado Ranch Dressing
DINE UPON REQUEST SM
In an effort to accommodate your individual preferences,
American Airlines is pleased to offer any of the entrees listed below
for your Dine Upon Request selection, complete with assorted fine Cheeses
and Cheesecake with seasonal Berry Topping, presented all at once,
at any time you wish during the flight.
Filet Mignon • Seafood Risotto
Roasted Chicken with Mixed Greens
Should you prefer a specific time for dining, please inform your flight attendant,
who will be happy to accommodate your specific request.
We apologize if occasionally your selection is not available.
